title.narrative: Implementation of DAPP partner activities supported

A number of DAPP partner meetings and of monitoring visits have been conducted in both Egypt and Morocco. Participation in relevant donor coordination fora and networks have taken place and contacts and networks with key stakeholders have been established.
DAPP programming in Morocco and Egypt enhanced

The strengthening of advisor capacity in Egypt and Morocco has contributed to an enhanced DAPP programming in both countries through programme support and monitoring and through coordination and networking with relevant stakeholders in both countries
